-- German Politicians Asked to Respect Pirates, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 2012-04-27T05:26:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-27/german-politicians-asked-to-respect-pirates-handelsblatt-says.html
German managers said politicians
and company executives should take the Pirate Party seriously, a
Forsa poll conducted for German business daily  Handelsblatt 
showed.  Two thirds of the 621 business managers surveyed said
lawmakers should consider forming governing coalitions with the
Pirate Party, while half said companies should acquaint
themselves with its political ideas, Handelsblatt said, citing
the poll.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
